eation## Non-Functional Requirements That Apply- **NFR-006** (compliance): EU sharers must provide GDPR consent before s
hortening.  Threshold: Zero URL shortening requests originating from EU IP addresses are processed without an explicit G
DPR consent flag.  Measurement: Middleware intercepts all shorten requests, verifies GDPR_consent=true for EU-origin IPs
; audit logs record consent status and origin; nightly compliance report aggregates violations for human review.- **NFR-
008** (security): Reject URLs exceeding 2048 characters and non-http(s) schemes with HTTP 400.  Threshold: Zero requests
 with URL length >2048 characters or non-http(s) schemes are rejected; all such requests must return HTTP 400.  Measurem
ent: Automated integration test harness runs on every deploy, submitting URLs of up to 3000 characters and various non-h
ttp(s) schemes (ftp, file, data, etc.) and asserting the response status code is 400; runtime request logs are monitored
 for any non-400 responses to over-long or unsupported scheme URLs.## Component ContractComponent: `comp-click-counter-i
